In a debug build, I get this warning on startup:

```
WARNING: Can't read data path preference. FOG will not be initialized: file /z/moz/l/toolkit/components/telemetry/core/Telemetry.cpp, line 1180
```

Let's remove it, since it's probably not of interest to people not working on Glean.
